First, I dont' think this works as AAXP.  AAXP skills are manaless and button based.  I am not aware of any that creates a scroll you can scribe in your book, and unless this skill were castable, it would not be made useful.  As a button, with zero mana cost, I would wager on a very long reset (like the 77min for MGB) in which case it would be ineffective in addressing healing issues.  Manaless and quick reset and suddenly we would be unstoppable as healers.  It is just too strong.<br>
<br>
