Crimson Legacy</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umikar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mikar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Puppy</span><br>  Posts: 66<br> <font color=#333399>(8/3/02 2:31:05 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=59.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Combined Percentage Based Healing Poll</span><hr size=1> Wizards outdamage rogues on many SoL raids. <br>
